Package: ESAListings
Type: Package
Title: An R Data package for U.S. Endangered Species Act Listed Species
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: person("Evans", "Michael", email = "mevans@defenders.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Michael Evans <mevans@defenders.org>
Description: The data included in this package was created using records from the U.S. Fish and Wildlife Service's (FWS)
 Environmental Conservation Online System (ECOS).  This database is the official agenc repository for publicly accessible
 information about species listed under the Endangered Species Act (ESA).  Extracted data in this package is related to
 taxanomic, geographic, and temporal information for all listed species.  The package includes a function to launch an
 interactive web app that can be used to explore this data.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.3.1)
License: BSD_2_clause + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
Dependencies:
  dplyr,
  DT,
  highcharter,
  leaflet,
  plotly,
  treemap,
  shiny,
  shinydashboard,
  viridis
